}}'''脑沟'''（Sulcus，复数为sulci），为[[大脑皮层|大脑皮层]]中呈现裂缝状的部位，与呈现隆起的回状结构[[脑回|脑回]]相对<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Toward a Common Terminology for the Gyri and Sulci of the Human Cerebral Cortex|url=https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fnana.2018.00093/full|last=ten Donkelaar|first=Hans J.|last2=Tzourio-Mazoyer|first2=Nathalie|date=2018|journal=Frontiers in Neuroanatomy|doi=10.3389/fnana.2018.00093|volume=12|language=en|issn=1662-5129|last3=Mai|first3=Jürgen K.|access-date=2021-06-01|archive-date=2021-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603025415/https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fnana.2018.00093/full|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Neuroscience For Kids - lobes of the brain|url=https://faculty.washington.edu/chudler/lobe.html|access-date=2021-06-01|work=[[华盛顿大学|华盛顿大学]]|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110063059/http://faculty.washington.edu/chudler/lobe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。出现脑回和脑沟的原因是，[[演化|演化]]过程中折叠结构使颅内相同容量下人类可以有更多[[大脑皮质|大脑皮质]]，而较低等的动物则脑沟脑回较少<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The cerebral sulci and gyri|url=https://thejns.org/focus/view/journals/neurosurg-focus/28/2/article-pE2.xml|last=Ribas|first=Guilherme Carvalhal|date=2010-02-01|journal=Neurosurgical Focus|issue=2|doi=10.3171/2009.11.FOCUS09245|volume=28|pages=E2|language=en-US|issn=1092-0684|access-date=2021-06-01|archive-date=2021-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602235900/https://thejns.org/focus/view/journals/neurosurg-focus/28/2/article-pE2.xml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

